          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By  author.  The measured cross-section correspond to",
                "the products recoiling in the forward direction plus  a",
                "small fraction of the backward recoiling products",
                "stopped in the thorium metal foil.  These small",
                "contributions were corrected for the recoil ranges of",
                "the fission products in thorium metal.  A  forward-",
                "to-backward (F/B) ratio equal to one was used to",
                "convert the measured yields into total yields.  The",
                "assumption of F/B ratio of unity will not affect the",
                "final yields by more than 10% in view of the measured",
                " F/B ratio of 1.1 for 16-O induced fission of 238-U."
              ]
            }
          ],
